Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it! I thought I had this match in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's one stubborn guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of that, my body is at its last breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's really gotten to bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, it's been a while since I've had this kind of passionate Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A game where we pit our full strength in one shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting excited, Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Duel with you is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too bad I had to fight you under these circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:02:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The End of a Painful Battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for this! While we're wasting time, Jounouchi's probably Dueling right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he loses, his soul will be taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but the map says it's around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's left is to find a small alley....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Some time ago, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s Claw of Hermos activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't feel it now at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Jounouchi is already....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's look for Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.... Varon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was settled now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not bad either, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's fought me this hard up until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rank number one without a doubt when it comes to stubbornness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're fighting such a fierce battle, yet their fighting spirit hasn't dropped in the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Duel...! This sort of passionate Duel...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is what I have been seeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to fight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost of activating Aura Armor is paying half of my Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I set two cards face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During my Standby Phase, I Special Summon Psychic Armor Head from the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I activate a Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix Gravitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? Don't tell me....!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Magic Card can Special Summon four Armor Monsters from the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Gauntlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overboost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Active Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PHOENIX GRAVITATION!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I praise you for fighting this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a real Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I will bet on my full power and defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's only one getting beat today, Varon. And that's {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open! Graverobber!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take one card from your Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...! Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take One Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, I draw one card from the Graveyard randomly and activate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one I choose is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beg you, please come give me power....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew he'd be able to bring it out again this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! I activate the effect of the Claw of Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuse with Big Bang Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang Dragon Blow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'm gonna use your own weapon against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... This is what I've been searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best Duel that makes me burn with anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the strongest Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've ever enjoyed a Duel this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! This will be the final turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning Knuckle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang Dragon Blow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a blast! It was the greatest Duel I ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Big Bang Dragon Blow's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing one Monster, all of the opponent's Monsters will be destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and its total Attack Power will be inflicted to the player's Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of who you're thinking of now, I always believed you'd return to me in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's my defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admittedly, I did show you my uncool side...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, I leave Mai to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,VARON!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were defeated, Varon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul shall also become food to our God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your turn shall come next, Mai Kujaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the darkness of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai, I'm the same. We're similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't live on if I can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something to appease my "vessel of victory"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that, Mai, is {\i0}you{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling is not meant to fight for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is to win for yourself. \NAren't you the one who said so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon did his best as a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's you, I won't allow anyone to belittle him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more hot-tempered than you usually are today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Varon an {\i1}enemy{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he definitely was an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But any Duelist who faces me head on with all he has...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have respect for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, come on over and fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't understand your feelings unless I fight you one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both Duel at full strength so we have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go easy on me like the last Duel, I won't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi, I leave Mai to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, hit me with everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Duelist, I'll also go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wish for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That light before must have been coming from Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be around here, but where the heck is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brother, don't you think it's a little strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There hasn't been anyone around here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that Doma's hand is already reaching out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't intend on letting us pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have the time to play around with smallfry like yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you won't step back and let us pass quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll forcefully open up a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Harpy Lady Cyber Bondage in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The damage I got from that last Duel is still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Blue Flame Swordsman in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit! I'm not seeing very well anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}C'mon, my body... Hang in there a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn... end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both my Harpy Lady and your Blue Flame Swordsman have an equal Attack Power of 1800.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, ending without doing anything is not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry. I'm not pulling my punches here. I already made up my mind about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fought seriously with Varon, I understood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While Dueling with him, we started to understand each other as we spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I really understood his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Mai, I will fight you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, my feelings will reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I want to feel what you're feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you could ever understand my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desire for victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having no choice but to continue winning...! My feelings....!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't understand until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to give up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is you're planning, I'm just going to crush you along with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon one more Harpy Lady Cyber Bondage in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I activate a Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claw of Earo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By equipping Claw of Earo, the Attack of Harpy increases by 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai's greatest specialty... the Harpy Lady Combo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Harpy attacks your Blue Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment Blue Flame Swordsman is destroyed, his Special Effect is activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Swordsman and the other Harpy Lady's Attack Power are both 1800.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? You have the resolve to attack with the same Attack Points, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do such a meaningless thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only attack if I know for sure I'll lower your Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a reverse card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai's deck isn't an Attack-Only Deck like Varon's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a much more well-balanced deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has a good variety of both Magic Cards and Trap Cards in her control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'm not careful, I'll lose any advantage I got in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll wake you up right now, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sacrifice Scapegoat in order to let Panther Warrior attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harpy Lady Pharaoh Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Trap Card can be activated only when there are two or more Harpy Ladies on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wings of fire will negate the opponent's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we had been able to continue before, I could have lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without telling Mai anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That won't do. This time I'll tell Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I sacrifice Flame Swordsman and I Summon Cybernetic Wyvern in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cybernetic Wyvern, attack Harpy Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At long last I can have a {\i1}real{\i0} Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Ability of the Claw of Earo activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card goes to the Graveyard, I can equip it to a Harpy Lady on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I will go without holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that boundary has appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you can no longer run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, without anyone interfering, we will fight until one of us falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I didn't plan on running.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This barrier takes out the darkness of one's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even Yugi couldn't hold off its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in this Duel, I'll rid you of the darkness in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! I Summon Harpy Lady Cyber Bondage in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my Harpy Ladies gain 500 Attack Points due to the Orichalcos Barrier's effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on Harpies, attack Cybernetic Wyvern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing, Direct Attack Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open! Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stubborn just as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just as I planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open! Nightmare Tri-Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever my opponent Summons a Monster in any other way than Normal Summoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Monster Copy Tokens on my field equal to the amount my opponent has.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpy Lady, attack a Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn, the Harpy Copy Tokens can't attack, so I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have fallen for the same trick as last time......
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little sad that you didn't learn from your previous mistakes, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. It's not like I don't know how to grow up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not falling for your bluffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no place to run! This time I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am not going to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, Mai, I swear to get you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a fierce battle of spirits, Jounouchi defeated Varon. But without resting, the Duel with Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} started.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to tell his feelings to Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}, who doesn't want to accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In these conditions, Jounouchi is standing in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of the battle with Varon, Jounouchi has damaged his body to the point where he can fall anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Jounouchi's feelings reach Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bitter Victory"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
